@1000881 = ~This scroll -- given to you by the Svirfneblin king -- gives you the ability to shape stone. The scroll is specifically attuned to the recent earthworks of the gnomes that broke through into the prison of the beast that threatens the town. Use this scroll to reseal the hole.~
