@1002173 = ~With the sphere's abrupt movement, the vision in the pool has changed. The city of Athkatla has been replaced by a hellish nightmare of ghouls and fiends. The sphere in the picture now rests in a horrible and polluted landscape.~ []
@1002199 = ~You... you have the key! Or, rather... the sword! Please... please give it to me and I can be rid of this illusionary form at last!~ [AERIEC7]
@1002207 = ~I thank you for your trust. This sword... it is actually a key that unlocks the chain that powers my horrible illusion.~ []
@1002208 = ~My... My hands... my skin, it's real again! Oh, thank you, Baervan! Oh, we must find Quayle... and stop Kalah before he does any more harm!~ [AERIEC8]
@1002210 = ~Wait here, then... I will go further into this citadel and will come back later.~ []
@1002212 = ~You would let me join you? Al-alright... come, let's find Quayle. Who knows what they've done to him...~ []
@1002213 = ~Beware, not all things here are illusions. Close your eyes and strike back only if it hurts you... Oh, bring Quayle back safely, would you? He... he's been very good to me...~ []
@1002220 = ~I think I knew Quayle... We may have traveled together in Baldur's Gate...~ []
@1002229 = ~Aegis Fang +3~
@1002254 = ~Then you shall have to come and visit me from time to time and tell me what you've learned. Go... go with my blessing, girl.~ []
@1002255 = ~... Alright. Take--Take care of the circus while I'm away.~ []
@1002294 = ~What choice have I? ... Aye, <CHARNAME>, I'll come.~ []
@1002302 = ~I don't need your excuses! ... I'm--I'm sorry, I--please, just give me some time to mourn.~ []
@1002303 = ~I don't want to get used to it! ... I'm--I'm sorry, I--please, just give me some time to mourn.~ []
