By means of this spell, the caster's body becomes blurred, shifting and wavering unpredictably. This distortion causes all missile and melee attacks against the caster to be made with a -3 penalty, and the caster also gains a +1 bonus to all of his saving throws. Multiple castings of Blur are not cumulative.~ []
