@1011060 = ~You're a man of the Church, Keldorn. How can you stay so calm amidst such a constant display of magic in this group?  I feel most unsettled at the sight of it.~ [VALYGA47]
@1011068 = ~Ahh, Cernd. Come to investigate for the Grand Druid, have you? You may tell him that his way is dead. We are the Druids of Shadow and he can do nothing.~ []
@1011071 = ~A name I remember for some reason, though not one I fear. Do you make claim to know better than Faldorn what should be done here?~ []
@1011073 = ~I hardly thought I'd see you timid, Haer'Dalis.~ []
