@1011138 = ~Ha! 'Twill be music to my ears to wrap this lute about your head, someday, my aging hound. Now go out there with your blade once again and make yourself useful, aye?~ []
@1011147 = ~~ [NOBL204]
@1011158 = ~  Touch me not... you are unclean.~ [NOBw202]
@1011174 = ~If you can escape, you must take our acorns to the Queen. Tell her of our plight in this creature's lair.~ []
@1011187 = ~Who? Is this worthy of my time? I doubt it is so. I will face this fool under the old rules, and when they are dead I will be secure. Come; let us seal your fate... and your mouth.~ [CEFALD11]
