@1011204 = ~The scourge has been purged? I can tell that the deed is done, for even now the land sighs relief. This has been a great service to nature and she shall not forget.~ [CERND72]
@1011268 = ~ Talking to you ain't worth the risk, no sir. Go away... please?~ []
@1011270 = ~This oddly murky oil would appear to increase the movement and combat capabilities of the imbiber by 100%. Thus, a movement rate of 9 becomes 18, and a character normally able to attack once in a round could attack twice. It has no effect upon spellcasting time, however. The duration of the effect is 5 turns.

Not Usable By:
 Wizard Slayer~ []
