(Conjuration/Summoning) 
Level: 7
Range: 40 yards 
Duration: 6 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: Special 
Saving Throw: None 
This spell is much like its 3rd level counterpart Monster Summoning I, except that this spell summons one to four 5 HD monsters. These monster(s) appear within spell range and attack the caster's opponents until the spell duration expires, or until they are slain.~ []
