@1016210 = ~I thank you, and I... I will tell you what I can when it is time. I am sorry... I am sorry to ask this of you, but it is my duty to do so. Come, let us go.~ []
@1016211 = ~Stand away, citizen!~ []
@1016212 = ~Thank you, I am glad to be back in your company. I only wish it were not under such circumstances. Come, we must go. I will explain more when it is time.~ []
