@1017241 = ~The Cloak of Displacement is a magical item that causes subtle shifts in the image of its wearer, by as much as six inches in any direction. Aside from being an effective defense in combat situations, it has also been the cause of serious eyestrain amongst fellow party members.

STATISTICS:

