Weight: 0
Launcher: Bow~ []
@1017538 = ~This arrow has a particularly debilitating effect on its victims as, upon impact, it explodes into a huge ball of fire and shrapnel, affecting all within the area. This explosion occurs even if the target is immune to the arrow's damage.

STATISTICS:

Special: 6D6 explosion upon impact (save vs. spell for half)
