Damage: 1D6
Damage type: missile (piercing)
Weight: 0
Launcher: Bow~ []
@1017540 = ~The Arrow of Fire is a magical arrow that will burst into flames as it is fired at an enemy. The effect is similar to an arrow doused in oil and set aflame.

