@1017643 = ~The long bow is similar to the short bow, except that the staff is about as high as the archer is, usually 6 to 6.5 feet. Though the long bow is slightly slower than the short bow, it has better range and is more accurate. This one has been enhanced with magical properties, giving it an air of perfection.

