@1017654 = ~When used, this wand will cough forth a huge, burning ball of fire that streaks out to the desired range (a maximum of 90 feet) and bursts in a fiery, violent blast. The fireball inflicts 6d6 points of damage, with all 1s counted as 2s. The victim(s) may make a save vs. wands in order to reduce the damage by half. The second ability of the wand is akin to the wizard spell 'Agannazar's Scorcher' in that a column of flame will streak towards the victim, inflicting 6d6 + 6 points of damage, with a successful save vs. wands reducing the damage by half.

