@1017655 = ~When used, white crystalline motes spray forth from the wand in a column towards the victim, striking him or her square in the chest with numbing force. The temperature inside the column is deadly, and causes 8d6 points of damage, with all 1s counted as 2s. A successful save vs. wands reduces the damage by half.

