@1017656 = ~The possessor of this wand is able to discharge six bolts of lightning. As each bolt passes through a creature, it does 3D6 points of damage, with a successful save vs. wands reducing the damage by half. The bolts will pass through their target and proceed to rebound off of any nearby surfaces until their energy is expended. The wand may target up to six different enemies.

