@1017657 = ~When used, this wand emits a gold beam of energy at its targets up to a maximum range of 90 feet, affecting a 15-foot radius. If the target creatures fail their save vs. wands, they will fall into a deep, comatose sleep for 2 turns. Almost anyone of moderate intelligence can learn how to use this wand.

