 Mage
 Thief
 Monk
 Beast Master~ []
@1018933 = ~The simplest and humblest of staff weapons, the quarterstaff is a length of wood ranging six to nine feet in length. High quality quarterstaves are made of stout oak and are shod with metal at both ends. This one is particularly special, as it has been imbued with magical enhancements. 

STATISTICS:

Damage: 1D6 + 1
THAC0: +1 bonus
Damage type: crushing
Weight: 4
