@1019034 = ~When used, this wand will summon 12 HD of monsters, which will appear within the area of effect and attack the user's enemies. The monsters will remain until the spell duration expires, or until the monsters are slain.

STATISTICS:

Effect: Summon 12 HD of monsters
Range: 20 ft
Duration: 2 turns
Requires: 9 Intelligence
Usable By:
 Mage
 Bard~ []
@1019043 = ~When used, this wand will cause a pillar of flame to shoot from the sky and strike the target of the invoker. The flames will do 8D6 damage to the target unless the target makes a save vs. wands, in which case it will take half damage. The wand has a limited amount of charges, and will be destroyed when they are all used.

STATISTICS:

Effect: Flamestrike
Damage: 8D6 (save vs. wands for half)
Range: 120 ft
Area: 1 creature
Requires: 9 Intelligence
Usable by:
 Cleric
 Druid~ []
@1019044 = ~Two Handed Sword, Cursed Berserking +3
This is a cursed sword which performs perfectly under every test, save in the heat of battle. Upon entering combat, the wielder will immediately go berserk, killing everything within reach until either calming down or falling unconscious. A very powerful sword, but one must decide whether or not it is worth the risk. Even after the battle fury has ended, this sword can only be removed via a Remove Curse spell.

STATISTICS:

THAC0: +3 bonus
Damage: 1D10 + 3
Damage type: slashing
Special:
