@1019727 = ~Boo is a fuzzy little hamster. While Minsc believes that Boo is a miniature giant space hamster, you are rather certain that the tiny rodent is just a normal hamster.~ []
@1019736 = ~I... I believe I have placed a proper name to your manner, now that I have experienced it up close. I should have thought you fond of anagrams, 'Terminsel.'~ []
@1019749 = ~You wound me, my dear... my heart beats only for you...~ []
@1019752 = ~Wake up, you! Wake up! Come on, we have to get outta here!~ [IMOEN01]
@1019753 = ~What... Imoen? What's going on?~ []
@1019754 = ~Who... who are you?~ []
@1019756 = ~Keep... keep your greaves on, I'll move when I'm ready.~ []
@1019765 = ~You'd better make yourself ready right quick, you goon! Don't you remember getting dragged here?~ []
@1019766 = ~You ain't seen nothin'.

(A sack of coin is handed to the guard.)~ []
@1019789 = ~It must be because he's been messing with our heads. I don't remember much, but I know it... it hurt. <CHARNAME>, I just have to get out of here.~ []
@1019800 = ~Come on, <CHARNAME>, don't make me think of it. He did the same to you, I think. I heard you screaming like it, anyway.~ []
@1019807 = ~Yeah, me too, but my head hurts the most. Yours too by the sound of the screaming. We just have to get out of here.~ []
@1019811 = ~We'll go, but I must know who is behind this.~ []
@1019915 = ~It isn't like a normal pain. <CHARNAME>, it's on the inside, like my bones made a little dagger and it won't go away.~ []
@1019925 = ~Mmmm... mayhap I'll be lookin' somewhere else, then.~ []
@1019933 = ~ Blasted beggar's immune!~ [KORGAN38]
@1019936 = ~~ []
@1019947 = ~I be havin' two l'il wee ones... no, FOUR wee ones... all wi' their starvin' mouths... er...~ []
@1019950 = ~Stop being like that! I know it's just because he messed with your head, but that excuse only goes so far.~ []
@1019955 = ~I begin to understand. The master has left my side for study of another. He seeks to awaken power... a study of life and death, but I cannot bear the roll of years.~ []
@1019962 = ~Good and good. We have to watch each other's back. It's weird too, my head hurts more when we split. I... I don't know why that is.~ []
@1019965 = ~No, no, NO! I'm not dying here! I'm not! Oh, my head hurts! I have to get to the surface! I have to go!~ [IMOENP61]
@1019966 = ~Ay, now, big 'un... would ye be a mite interested in buyin' a few wares at th' barest prices in Athkatla?~ []
@1019983 = ~I see my eye for a potential customer has not failed me. Here, let me show you some of the goods I have acquired... just for you.~ []
@1019992 = ~I will not be the only one to lose my head here today! Dynaheir... My charge and friend... she is... she is dead and I am a failure as her guard!~ []
@1019993 = ~... They... they killed her as I watched, you see? I know not who they were, but... but I will redeem myself!~ []
@1020002 = ~What... yes but... but... alright. Boo tells me that I am raving again. I did not notice a difference, but I shall heed his words nonetheless.~ []
@1020009 = ~Oh, my... you're the biggest Big Folk I think I've ever seen!~ []
@1020018 = ~Don't ask questions better left to aged sages. Boo is quick and evasive and there is ever so much of Minsc to search; there is no hope of getting us apart.~ []
@1020020 = ~Boo is my animal companion, and while some smaller rangers might compensate for their size by traveling with bears or wolves, I prefer the subtleties provided by a miniature giant space hamster! Yes, subtle!~ []
@1020032 = ~Oh, but I am sure you would be interested if you were but aware! Look, here... turnips of all sorts and varieties. Is that not the true spice of the exotic?~ []
@1020037 = ~Uh... excuse me, I'll be on my way.~ []
@1020041 = ~You will learn many harsh realities out here, but you will also learn to deal with them. Or you may die. One or the other.~ []
@1020043 = ~Thanks for your support... I think.~ []
@1020044 = ~My injuries sting, but... I think it is mostly my pride that hurts. But we did well enough in our last battle, did we not? I'll wager we may outlive the season if we are careful.~ [JAHEIR46]
@1020045 = ~Why, you have turnip stew. Boiled turnips, turnip salad, turnip and eggs! You can string turnips together and make a turnip necklace.~ []
@1020047 = ~Um... I'm really not interested in turnips, actually.~ []
@1020053 = ~You wear the scars of battle with pride, Anomen, like one who truly believes his cause.~ [JAHEIR54]
@1020065 = ~Uh... well, I -~ []
@1020068 = ~Er, thank you... I think I have to be going, now.~ []
@1020070 = ~Well, don't you forget, now. Jan Jansen: he'll have what a fine adventuresome sort like yourself is looking for. Just tell him Cousin Kylie sent you!~ []
@1020083 = ~He's hard to miss. He's usually in the Government District... better coin there. Not many gnomes wandering the streets of Athkatla, anyway.~ []
@1020097 = ~Perhaps, though I doubt you would find the trip back to the cities a peaceful one.~ []
@1020103 = ~In the next chamber there are four portals. Each of these portals releases little cackling fiends which try to kill me.~ []
@1020104 = ~I am not weak, Jaheira, and you were as likely to be hurt as I.~ [AERIE69]
@1020105 = ~Karajah's Leather Armor +3~ []
@1020122 = ~Not within battle, no, but I gather your black and white views extend well beyond that. There is gray as well.~ []
@1020123 = ~Gray? Gray is not a color, it is the blurring of another. Gray is indecision, and I have no time for it.~ []
@1020129 = ~You... don't seem like any creature I've encountered before.~ []
@1020143 = ~It was quite silly... it was obvious that whatever the gnome was trying to do wasn't working.~ []
@1020147 = ~... I think I passed out. When I woke up, I had been turned into this... into this... monstrosity!~ []
@1020150 = ~I... I don't know what to do! My son didn't come into the tent with me and I'm frightened to think what may have happened to him!~ []
@1020152 = ~My... my name's Hannah. I came to the circus with my son, although he didn't come into the tent with me. Oh, please help me!~ []
@1020162 = ~They... they're not people! They're vicious and dangerous! I've seen them kill people... you must stop them!~ []
@1020163 = ~I'll try. Tell me... do you know where this 'Kalah' is?~ []
@1020176 = ~I don't know. If you are of sufficient strength, it is possible the cage may be broken. If not, you may have to search for whatever key it might need.~ []
@1020179 = ~The hunt for Valygar Corthala.

Hervo mentioned that Valygar had numerous friends in the Amnish military, as he was a scout for them at one point. He remembered one friend in particular... a woman by the name of Suna Seni. This is the same woman who sought me out recently with a group of thugs... although Hervo doesn't seem to think this is connected to Valygar, I am not so sure.~ []
@1020191 = ~A well thought and calculated plan, though I do not recall you being so cold. Perhaps I have had some memory loss myself.~ []
@1020212 = ~Forgive me the curiosity, but you are quite alien to me. You are not of this place, and do not fit into the natural order, at least not by design.~ []
@1020221 = ~Or perhaps you enjoy the discord of chaos because you have not found that niche as yet. We shall see.~ []
@1020227 = ~Ahh, you have quite the way of inspiring comrades. Certainly such an act would let you sleep soundly at night. Your 'friends' will... watch over you intently.~ []
@1020234 = ~Ooo, such delicious fire, though better it was turned on an enemy. I would be your ally, Jaheira; your strength might even bring you respect among my kind.~ []
@1020237 = ~I am not to be swayed by your words, creature. I know too much of you and your kind.~ []
@1020243 = ~Do you wish me dour and sour like most others? No, I say not. The animals run and play without care, and I would too... if such a thing would not squish Boo flat.~ []
@1020249 = ~Eh, well... no... but it sounds sharp and painful and I always reserve such things for freaks that might steal those squirrels' nuts!~ []
@1020254 = ~Unnatural... yes. I struggle to understand the differences in magic that have been presented to me. How do you feel about it, Jaheira? Are they not all cut of the same vile shroud?~ [VALYGA62]
@1020270 = ~Er, yes, whatever you wish.~ []
@1020277 = ~You look quite interested in the local flora, Jan.~ [JAHEIR50]
@1020279 = ~Oh, yes indeed. It reminds me of my cousin, Tyllie Fleetknees, and the garden she had at the foot of a dryad tree in the Forest of Wyrms. I tell you, she went up expecting well-aerated soil, yet did she get a surprise? Oh yes indeed! Why, I remember it like it was burned into my memory with a flaming stick, which was very close to the truth actually...~ [JANJAN61]
@1020282 = ~Er... yes?~ []
@1020293 = ~Ahh... of course.~ []
@1020298 = ~Hahaha... you're not what? You're not my beast? Oh, but you are, all of you are, don't you see?~ [KALAH08]
@1020301 = ~Well done, my friend! Truly, I doubted that you would survive to meet me. Welcome to my domain. I regret that my hospitality will result in your deaths.~ [KALAH03]
@1020303 = ~Little Aerie, is that you? I have no eyes, no eyes!~ []
@1020304 = ~You there! I am not what I seem to be! It is I... Quayle.~ []
@1020330 = ~... Alright. Take--Take care of the circus while I'm away.~ []
@1020336 = ~I will yell if I wish, and I will make damn sure our enemies here me! We must hurry and find... we...~ []
@1020337 = ~I will not! If you do not care enough to hurry then perhaps another should lead! Someone that will make sure our fallen are avenged! Someone who... who...~ []
@1020338 = ~We must gather ourselves and what equipment we can for the war to come. We must be ready to avenge... and fight...~ []
@1020339 = ~I... I am sorry, I have been thinking too much of... of Khalid. I was in shock before, but...~ []
@1020342 = ~We will have revenge for all wrongs in time.~ []
@1020343 = ~I... I agree, though I shall try not to be fixated on such things. All will be dealt with in time. I will see to it.~ []
@1020344 = ~I will not forget just like that. I will... bide my time. In the end we will deal justice to those that deserve it. Patience is all it will take.~ []
@1020345 = ~Yes, in time. I will try to maintain my composure through this.~ []
@1020346 = ~Nnn... no!~ [JAHEIR70]
@1020347 = ~Nnn... No! NO!! Wh... what?~ []
@1020350 = ~Restless dreams. I have them myself on occasion.~ []
@1020351 = ~N-no, there is something very wrong. More and more I feel Khalid's absence. I... I thought myself stronger than this.~ []
@1020352 = ~I... I was. I stood beside Khalid in a battle long since won, only this time, he did not survive. There was... nothing I could do.~ []
@1020355 = ~There is no weakness in sorrow.~ []
@1020361 = ~This powerful elixir is similar to the potion of heroism in that it effectively raises the imbiber's level, but it can also be used by all character classes. It affects hit points, THAC0 and thieving abilities, although it does not raise the backstab multiplier. Its effects are applied to the user's base abilities, before any attribute modifiers are added.

STATISTICS:

