@1020893 = ~Ah, yes. The fellow who was bein' such a problem for the Cowled Wizards to apprehend, eh? Ye'd be interested in findin' this man, then?~ [GAELEN17]
@1020902 = ~Why don't I take you there right now? Unless you have some reason for not wantin' to come along?~ [GAELEN20]
@1020910 = ~I can handle myself in a fight, if that's what you're asking.~ []
@1020914 = ~Hah! I have no interest in settin' up a trap. It be more profitable to serve. I will speak no more... come with me and you can decide whether to enter me house.~ [GAELEN22]
@1020929 = ~Aye, I'll be doing that quick as ye blink. I'll tell ye straight that I know a powerful group that can be helping ye. They can be findin' the wizard and the young woman both, they can.~ [GAELEN27]
@1020943 = ~Anomen's Judgement.

We have arrived at the Order's headquarters for Anomen's trial. I am to go inside with him and observe the judgement as it takes place.~ []
@1020949 = ~I don't have that much money... how am I supposed to raise such a fare?~ []
@1020969 = ~You cannot control more than 5 monsters at any given time.~
@1020981 = ~Ah! Ye be havin' it, already, does ye? A great an' good thing it is. I will tell ye of the man who can be helpin' ye.~ [GAELEN31]
