@1021036 = ~Very good. Just so you be knowing, you be goin' to the Shadowmaster Aran Linvail. Step carefully, me <LADYLORD>, the Shadowmaster does not suffer fools gladly.~ [GAELEN32]
@1021038 = ~This person ye was seen with... have ye joined forces with her?~ []
@1021064 = ~An excellent choice, my <LADYLORD>. You'll find that I offer many things not to be found elsewhere in Athkatla... and if they are, you'll not find them at a lower price.~ []
@1021067 = ~~ []
@1021068 = ~~ []
@1021069 = ~~ []
@1021079 = ~I'll not let it be, Cernd. The wizard killed Suna in such an offhand fashion... he cared not a spit for her life. Doesn't he deserve to suffer for it?~ [VALYGA64]
@1021082 = ~Well I know it. And you have no need to worry... I shall pay the closest attention to every step that brings me closer to that foul mage!~ []
@1021087 = ~I... damn you, druid, just leave me be!~ []
@1021091 = ~You remind me more and more as each day passes of what makes magic vile and evil, wizard.~ [VALYGA48]
@1021095 = ~I cower before nothing! I merely showed caution before approaching Lavok... someone possessing far more power than you!~ []
@1021098 = ~You did what you could and that is enough. I appreciate it, but I also worry that you suffered worse.~ []
@1021101 = ~Um... Let's just get moving.~ []
@1021105 = ~The event is behind us, but I doubt it is truly over with. We will have to find Irenicus to really put the matter to rest. At least, that is my aim.~ []
@1021109 = ~You picked an odd profession if you really desire to settle down.~ []
@1021113 = ~It was like that for a long time, but I always felt I should do more. Balance needed to be... encouraged. I wouldn't let it happen again.~ []
@1021115 = ~You would not allow what to happen again?~ []
@1021118 = ~I mean... for the good of the party.~ []
@1021119 = ~I... This may be a bad time or not, but you asked a question of me and I brushed it aside. I would speak of it now... if you still wish to hear.~ [JAHEIR81]
@1021121 = ~I... if you wish. I had just thought... never mind. We shall continue as we are.~ []
@1021122 = ~I did not want to press if you wanted to remain silent.~ []
@1021126 = ~I did, but I... it is not important enough to keep aside. I would rather such things be talked of openly. I know much of you, but you know little of me.~ []
@1021136 = ~I thank you for those words. I find myself drawing strength from you in our close quarters. It has been... a great help.~ []
@1021137 = ~I... I am sorry. We should continue on.~ []
@1021140 = ~Your role as druid?~ []
@1021142 = ~I... I though we had come to a point where such talk was valuable to... Never mind, I shall not pursue what is obviously lost.~ []
@1021143 = ~As Harper and as druid. They are complimentary, despite bards being thought the Harper standard-bearers. Both seek balance over all. I... I think I have done so.~ []
@1021149 = ~I think... I think I am the one out of balance, not you. I think... well, I think many things. I... I need more time to consider this.~ []
@1021150 = ~I'm afraid you'll have to indulge my silence for a time longer. I... I apologize for interrupting you.~ []
@1021160 = ~I am becoming used to the aftermath of death, but I will not forget what must be avenged. There must be closure. I must do this even as I... as we... move on.~ []
@1021167 = ~Yes... what is your point?~ [VALYGA53]
@1021186 = ~You'll have to excuse me if I stare, as you're not quite what I was expecting. From all I've been told, I was expecting someone... larger.~ [RENAL02]
@1021193 = ~You'll have to excuse me if you're not quite what I was expecting. From all I've been told I expected something... grander.~ [RENAL03]
@1021220 = ~My name is Renal, as I'm sure you've been told. Renal 'Bloodscalp'... a little nickname I've earned over time. Rather grisly, but it keeps the fearful in line.~ []
@1021236 = ~If it does, and Mae'Var proves to be guilty... and of that I have little doubt... then you will have proven yourself to me fully.~ []
@1021240 = ~Mmm. Interesting. Very well... I agree to do as you ask.~ []
@1021242 = ~You are interested in acquiring more than the simple goodwill of the Shadow Thieves, I see. I do not blame you... I would feel the same way.~ []
@1021260 = ~Excellent. I knew this would work out for the best. You remind me a bit of myself when I first arrived here.~ []
@1021266 = ~I'd like to know why one of your own men doesn't do it for you.~ []
@1021278 = ~ I am most pleased with the efforts this party is making... I am proud to be a part of it.~ [MAZZY03]
@1021280 = ~ I trust that this current... direction... we are on will not continue.~ [MAZZY04]
@1021281 = ~ I am warning you... as a defender of the right, I will not tolerate this sort of behavior!~ [MAZZY05]
@1021284 = ~ <yawn>  I am willing to continue, if needed... but I would vote to stop and rest.~ [MAZZY08]
@1021292 = ~Yes, I have the evidence you need in these writings. It seems that Mae'Var has been making overtures to the Night Masks.~ []
