@1021954 = ~These bracers appear to be Bracers of Specialization, but when donned, bind the wearers wrists together, making it quite difficult to wield a weapon or cast a spell. Such bracers are sometimes offered as rewards for services rendered by the drow. The recipient, believing them to be very powerful, will often don them before examining them. At this point, the drow find it amusing to conjure a hook horror.

