Special: Miscast Magic affects victim on each successful hit
Miscast Magic: Any spellcasting creature that is affected by this spell has its casting ability severely disabled. When the creature attempts to cast a spell it has an 80% chance of failure. Creatures can save vs spells to avoid the affect, but do so at a -2 penalty. 
Weight: 6
