@1022020 = ~Staves of Striking are made by the Gold Elves of Drelagara on Evermeet. The staves have a life of their own, and jump to attack in their bearer's hands. The elven craftsmen rarely sell them to other races, but these powerful melee weapons do surface occasionally in Faerun. However, each attack made with the staff uses a charge, causing it to consume itself when no charges remain.

