@1022028 = ~I did not intend for you to cripple them; that will come later.~ []
@1022031 = ~I will honor my deal, giving you exactly what I have promised. I will deliver you directly to where she is, bypassing these foolish thieves.~ []
@1022033 = ~You need not be so bitter. You will benefit from all of this in the long run. Already you have helped me, and I will show gratitude in the end.~ []
@1022046 = ~You have arrived, but all is not well. Your employers ask you to collect 20,000 gold; I will deal for 15,000, so return when you have your spending under control.~ []
@1022047 = ~I see. It would seem you have enjoyed turning the tables on your former employers. You have given them a bruise, though it will not cripple them.~ []
@1022048 = ~This attack will have alarmed the guild, such that they fortify certain places. That draw of manpower will weaken others. Overall, my position is stronger.~ []
@1022049 = ~Now I ask for more specific tasks that will disrupt the guild further. I give you a choice: I have two tasks, each will require a different kind of person.~ []
@1022050 = ~Choose; they cannot both be done. One is... unseemly, so if you claim to be 'good' you should choose the second, a sickly hero's task. Which do you prefer?~ []
@1022055 = ~Take this cloak and dagger and go kill Senior Armagaran Vulova. When he is dead, put the cloak and dagger in the fountain in his house.~ []
@1022059 = ~Murder is not what I was expecting.~ []
@1022062 = ~And make your next visit earlier. I do not enjoy the sunlight. I have... very delicate skin.~ []
@1022072 = ~Assassin~ []
@1022081 = ~ I... I am wounded, terribly! I need to be healed if I am to continue on much longer!~ [MAZZY15]
@1022085 = ~Oh happy day! You have come to collect Minsc and Boo and together we shall put our collective boots to our enemies!~ []
@1022115 = ~I await your instructions.~ []
@1022134 = ~Very well... what is your plan?~ []
@1022135 = ~I have my own plans... out of my way.~ []
@1022136 = ~I... I see, my <PRO_LADYLORD>. Very well.~ []
@1022137 = ~Staff Mace +2~
@1022139 = ~This amulet contains a greenstone embedded within a gold setting. When activated, the greenstone protects the wearer from all forms of mind attacks, including psionics. (note: it does not confer COMPLETE immunity to psionics)

STATISTICS:

Special Abilities:
This amulet confers upon the wearer protection against many forms of mind-control magic, such as Charm, Confusion, Fear, Domination, Know Alignment, Hold, Stun, Psionics, Sleep and Feeblemind. However, the protection effect uses one charge each time it is used, and will only last for 1 turn.

Not Usable by:
 Wizard Slayer~ []
