@1023632 = ~"Well, the crew all did agree with her
They threw Johnny o'erboar'
And that's why you'll hear Johnny cryin'
When the winds they start to roar!~ []
@1023637 = ~"An' that's why you'll hear Johnny cryyyyyin'
When the wiiiinds they start tooooo roooaaar!"~ []
@1023641 = ~Sailors an' thieves... Athkatla be full o' them both!~ []
@1023642 = ~The Sea's Bounty be a nice pub an' all, but if ye steps outside, ye be as likely to have yer pocket picked as not.~ []
@1023645 = ~The Sea's Bounty be a fine an' grand place. <hic!>  Hmm... where's my coin purse?~ []
@1023646 = ~It is good to see you again. I had hoped you'd return. There's little here for me. Do you... do you still need another party member?~ [NALIA94]
@1023663 = ~The sailors around here are so handsome... but their language is simply atrocious! I cannot decide if this tavern is worth my time.~ []
@1023670 = ~Yes, I remember. Well, you may be right... perhaps we should ask them?~ []
@1023672 = ~Errr... alright. Foul intruders! We shall stop you for our master!~ []
@1023679 = ~They say this be the City of Coin... and it be the last place ye want to be if ye have none.~ []
@1023681 = ~I don't know why they have one o' the guards here in the slums... he gets paid so much money he might as well be blind, aye?~ []
@1023682 = ~I've heard more than a few stories about that there circus over on the promenade... but I don't believe a none o' it.~ []
@1023684 = ~Just a word o' caution... ye don't want to be dealin' too much with Lehtinan, there. He's the evil sort, an' I don't use that term lightly.~ []
@1023694 = ~This is the pleasure room... you're welcome to join us. Or sleep for a while. We all end up asleep, here, eventually...~ []
@1023695 = ~... MmmMmmm... my, but you are a pretty one? Would you care to join me, my pretty elf?...~ []
@1023697 = ~... Care to sample some of our Black Lotus, my good friend?...~ []
@1023698 = ~No thank you, good sir. I've... already attempted the experience once before.~ []
@1023700 = ~... HahaHAhahaHAHA...(giggle)~ []
@1023701 = ~... I think Lehtinan is the most DARLING man to make this place for us...~ []
@1023702 = ~... MMMmmm... all I can think of is those slaves in the pit... what was that gorgeous one's name? Hendak? MMmmm...~ []
@1023703 = ~... I've won twice today betting on Hendak, that fighting slave... wonderful man, that...~ []
@1023704 = ~I wonder if they're going to start another fight soon? Hmmm... maybe I'll just take a quick nap, instead...~ []
@1023705 = ~This sort of place would normally be beneath me... but it has some of the most wonderful entertainments, you see. If you know how to ask for them.~ []
@1023708 = ~Ahhh... I do miss the days of being fabulously entertained in the back rooms. But Hendak does still run a fine place.~ []
@1023713 = ~Have you seen that huge sphere? How absolutely dreadful. I seem to remember something about it... some story about a wizard? Hm. Whatever.~ []
@1023715 = ~That's the only thing I hate about coming here... beggars! Beggars everywhere!~ []
@1023721 = ~I've won several matches with those dogs of Surly's! What a delightfully vicious little game!~ []
@1023727 = ~I am the keeper of the creatures that fight in the pit. My wild ones do well... our record is excellent, especially my lovely Tabitha, here. Isn't that right, my precious?~ []
@1023746 = ~Champion's Strength~ []
@1023753 = ~I warn you, however... if you dare to tell so much as one other person about this place... we will know about it. And you will suffer the consequences. Now go.~ []
@1023759 = ~If you have, then I am ready to add my skills to your repertoire. What say you?~ []
@1023763 = ~I... well, you're the one that knows them! They're not going to kill you just because you're looking for the whereabouts of a spy... er... thief. Bah!~ []
@1023767 = ~You may dislike me... whoever you are... but would you not even take a small risk for Montaron? A faultless soul, and likely being tortured even as we speak!~ []
@1023778 = ~Forget it... I'm not falling for that trick.~ []
@1023784 = ~My... my name is Renfeld... (groan)  I have been poisoned... I beg you to take me to... friends... they have a building not far away from here... please, I beg you!~ []
@1023789 = ~It is... no trick! I am dying... please, I ask for your help!~ []
