@1034672 = ~A shield of the elite Calimport Standing Dragoons mercenary company, a group long since disbanded due to political backstabbing. Having the best of equipment, their shields were extremely light and powerfully protective in combat. The size of the shield precludes the use of the shield hand for anything else.

