@1036384 = ~The Tallassans needed to be put in their place! This is better in the long term!~ []
@1036388 = ~Now we have the beginnings of a holy war, where both sides will not back down from insult! There will be much more death when their numbers are both reinforced.~ []
@1036392 = ~I see that you are no paladin of the Order after all. Just as I suspected! A brutish lout who cannot handle the competition, just as your father was!~ []
@1036394 = ~Speak not of my father! And I will not sit idly by and watch as you bribe and cajole your way into... into... what? <CHARNAME>?! What are you doing here?!~ []
@1036396 = ~I fear your welcome will be a little cold, <CHARNAME>. We are still feeling the effects of the war you have let begin.~ []
@1036402 = ~Because this is evil... this will take you down a path that will destroy you forever!~ []
@1036409 = ~I... I had intended to do this myself. There is no need for both of us to perform a necessary evil, my love. But I... I will not stop whatever you intend.~ []
@1036410 = ~Put up your sword, then, Saerk! It grieves me that it has come to this, but it is my own fault that this did not occur sooner! For Moira... and my father!!~ []
@1036411 = ~Aye... aye, you speak the right of it, my love. It... it is the guilt that crushes me beneath its weight. That I walked away from my duty and my abominable father took it up!~ []
@1036412 = ~There is an evil in my heart, I have always known this and I spoke of it to you. Hate and anger, twisted and black... and I... I cannot control it.~ []
@1036413 = ~My heart tells me to kill this demon... and my guilt will be assuaged. I... I cannot live like this, <CHARNAME>... at any moment all I believe in I could betray...~ []
@1036419 = ~I... I would put an end to this hate, my love. If I could. It destroyed my father, and now it threatens to destroy me. But yet I do not know if I can...~ []
@1036420 = ~I love you, too... but 'tis already done. My family is dead and I am destroyed. I am sorry... but my black heart demands nothing less than this demon's death!~ []
@1036421 = ~Then... then that is enough for me. I will live on the hope that your love... will one day quench my hate. I thank you, <CHARNAME>, for... for stopping me.~ []
@1036424 = ~In the pursuit of coin, you not only ruined my father... but you killed an innocent girl. You have a daughter, do you not, Saerk?~ []
@1036425 = ~... err... yes...~ []
@1036426 = ~I hope you will be able to look your daughter in the eye when you are in prison... and I hope you will think on what you have done ere you go to the gods for judgement.~ []
@1036427 = ~... I...~ []
@1036429 = ~I am sorry, my love, for all of this disturbance. You have a quest to attend to... and I intend to be there to assist you. Now... and forever more...~ []
@1036430 = ~Together. Together, yes... but do you love me, <CHARNAME>? Am I only your companion, or will I have your strength to draw on?~ []
@1036433 = ~Then there is nothing more that needs to be said. I will follow the dictates of my heart, though it leads me into darkness. I... I am sorry, my love.~ []
@1036437 = ~<CHARNAME>... I do truly love you, as I have said so many times before. But it is not enough to assuage my dark heart.~ []
@1036438 = ~I... I have ruined myself in the Order. There is no place for me there, anymore. I... I am too much my father's son.~ []
@1036439 = ~I must go away, <CHARNAME>. I must go somewhere into seclusion and see if I can live with this hate... try to... to quench it. But I cannot stay with you.~ []
@1036443 = ~You there! You came in with this fool... what are your intentions?!~ []
@1036445 = ~Only to tell you that you will pay for what you have done... according to the law.~ []
@1036453 = ~I... I am sorry, m'<LADYLORD>. All of the Delryns are dead an' gone, I fear... Lord Cor was killed by 'is son, that failed knight. Then 'is son went an' killed himself. Pity, that. Tsk.~ []
@1036455 = ~I am sorry, my <LADYLORD>... there is no one available at the house. A former knight of the Order of the Radiant Heart broke into the house recently and murdered the merchant, Saerk.~ []
@1036459 = ~A morning star consists of a wooden shaft topped with a metal head made up of a spiked iron sheath. Morning stars have an overall length of about four feet. Such weapons have round, oval, or cylindrical shaped heads studded with spikes. Extending from most morning star heads, regardless of design, is a long point for thrusting. Enchantments have made this morning star lighter, faster, and far more deadly than a normal weapon of its kind.

