Basalin was a large man, rumored to be a were-bear. He long wielded the sword Albruin in the protection of his village, slaying giant spiders which plagued the area. The sword protected him from their poison, and also allowed him to see invisible Red Wizards who controlled some of the more fantastic variants. The reason for their enmity is unknown.

