@1039724 = ~What do you know of my capture!~ []
@1039725 = ~I know more than your brain could hold in a lifetime. There is so much beneath your nose; so much you do not see. Why, even Imoen escaped your notice.~ []
@1039732 = ~I grow tired of this conversation. You have asked your questions and made your threats, and I have indulged them both. Now this will end.~ []
@1039734 = ~There is more I should ask. You could shed so much light on my situation.~ []
@1039740 = ~Irenicus allowed himself to be overcome in his rage. He has recovered, and is no one's prisoner. Your Imoen is not as strong, though I am told she has... potential.~ []
@1039743 = ~You'll not walk away from me so easy!~ []
@1039751 = ~You have our thanks for destroying our collars. If you are in search of the newest captives, you can find them in the northwest part of the complex. Perhaps they will have a way to save us from this forsaken prison.~ []
@1039753 = ~As though on the wings of pigs I have been granted a fanciful tale of daring and danger amidst the wood. Are you the servants of the wild who have restored the balance to this place?~ [CERND66]
@1039754 = ~Hello and well met to you. I am Cernd, though my identity is surely no secret after the fuss I have caused here.~ [CERND01]
@1039755 = ~Well, I take it that your grim visages are to be my escorts to whatever fate the merchants have decided upon? I have feared your coming.~ [CERND02]
@1039756 = ~Hello again! Have you come here on business or just to sample the rich beauty of nature? I find myself doing much of the latter as Verthan has handled the transition to leadership very well.~ [CERND79]
@1039757 = ~ This is the land of merchants, good friend... a veritable paradise for those with coin.~ [FEMER03]
@1039760 = ~Your words baffle, though I am certain some insult has taken place. Keep your distance from this one, Boo, he is definitely unstable.~ []
@1039761 = ~Those dwarves that attacked us; I read about them when you were skipping out of lessons back in Candlekeep.~ [IMOENJ59]
@1039762 = ~Please hurry to the keep and find Daleson. I don't have anything else to tell you for now unless... unless you want me to come with you!~ [NALIA65]
@1039763 = ~If that is what you wish... it will be safer than waiting here. I will wait outside by the palisade.~ [NALIA95]
@1039764 = ~Boots of Elvenkind
