@1060895 = ~I... I am sorry. I did not wish to disturb you with this. In my... my dream we WERE under attack, in a battle we had long since won, but it was different.~ []
@1060896 = ~Ah, I understand. Most of us would tend towards equilibrium. It would require effort to pull in one direction or another.~ []
@1060907 = ~You have WON!!!~ []
@1060926 = ~But I will speak no more, out of respect for your... what was it again? Ah yes, your little stick.~ []
@1060929 = ~Burn did the sky with rage and fire, until plucked from the air by the hand of a King. He saw the weak and scarred underbelly, he saw the path to the source of the fire.~ []
@1060950 = ~This is not a matter of character. Some things are deeper, and though you can take the leopard far from the jungles, he still has his spots.~ []
