@1060984 = ~I will tell you one thing, my <LADYLORD>... I can create the finest of musical horns -- the dwarf knows not this art.~ []
@1060990 = ~I see you have the silver horn. Hmmm... and a diamond! If you wish, for 2,000 gold pieces I could create a more powerful instrument!~ []
